<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.classicshell.net/forum/viewtopic.php?t=7062&amp;p=30265#p30265"><![CDATA[
HIIIII Friends, I am uploading my custom made 'Flying Kiss Lady' Start Button for you guys.....<br /><br />there are two sizes....small &amp; a bit large....<br />if you need a different size, simply open the larger image in any image processing program [like faststone image viewer] lock the aspect ratio &amp; resize it.....after that save it in .png format...............<br /><br />please check following check box while applying this button--<br /><br />*go to start menu settings..<br />*click on 'start button' tab...<br />*now check the box &quot;align to corner of the screen&quot;.....<br /><br />it gives the best fit to this button.....<br /><br />you can save the .png images by right click on them......<br /><br />Enjoy......&amp; please comment..........<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.classicshell.net/forum/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=16074">TheOlderNe0</a> — Tue Nov 08, 2016 1:52 am</p><hr />
]]></content>
